window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A complete trilogy and a bonus standalone, all-in-one!</p> <p>Barrett Bradshaw was always a bookworm, but no amount of reading would prepare him for his childhood crush turning him into a vampire. Even more absurd, it turns out that he was never fully human at all.</p> <p>Now enrolled at Nosferatu Academy, an institution in the demiplane known as the Netherveil, founded for the sole purpose of educating the next generation of vampires, Barrett finds himself dealing with cocky rivals, quirky love interests, eccentric teachers, and a new taste for blood. Also, it turns out that even the great Count Dracula expects big things from him...</p>"; 
